  "title": "Sales Engineer (HVAC)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our Client:</strong></p><ul><li>Up to $7,000, aws, and Commission</li><li>Office Hours, 8:30am – 5:30pm</li><li>Changi</li><li>Building Service Industry</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Drive the specification of EC fans in HVAC project tenders for both new builds and retrofit projects.</li><li>Build strong relationships with M&E consultants and design firms.</li><li>Serve as the main contact for consultants.</li><li>Coordinate with the marketing team to deliver regular product presentations.</li><li>Identify new business opportunities and stay updated on market trends, competitor activities, and upcoming projects.</li><li>Conduct technical presentations and training on EC fan solutions and energy-efficiency benefits.</li><li>Work with internal teams to ensure timely and accurate technical documentation.</li><li>Prepare reports on specification progress, sales pipeline, and market insights.</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or Degree in Mechanical / Electrical Engineering.</li><li>Minimum 3 years of experience in HVAC industry, preferably in consultant sales</li></ul><p></p><p>For interested applicants, please click \"Quick Apply”</p><p></p><p>We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates would be notified.</p><p></p><p>By submitting your personal data and/or resume, you will be deemed to have agreed and consented to us collecting, using, retaining, and disclosing your personal information to prospective employers for their consideration.</p><p></p><p>Elsa Adam | EA Reg No: R22109576</p><p>JTE Recruit Pte Ltd | EA Lic No: 14C7215</p>",
